{"tid":2193063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩警展示沒有警員照片及編號的「委任證」，柴灣工廈保安拒絕其入內並報警","createTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T04:54:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b64a3199fbed6906e9bcebd3de5dda3bfdecbd07","tid":2193063,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548354-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548354-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=bd9fb025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548354-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c4595ed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548354-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，早前接獲報案指，有2名報稱警員的男子上周二進入柴灣一幢大廈，懷疑是冒警，經進一步了解後，確認2人為港島總區刑事總部人員。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，2名便衣探員當晚就一宗刑事案件，到訪柴灣康平街華裕閣地下大堂以作調查，進入大廈後曾向管理員展示委任證，完成調查後便離開。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，一向尊重市民應有權利，任何人如對展示的委任證或宣稱的警察身份有懷疑，可與附近的警署或致電999與警方聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n東區區議員陳榮泰早前在社交網站表示，柴灣泳池一帶某樓宇日前有2名自稱警察的男子要求內進，保安員查問2人身份時，2人展示沒有警員照片及編號的委任證，保安員拒絕讓他們進入。"},{"pid":"9fcc0ceb71b112b72c20cb1663c1a7f272c49f63","tid":2193063,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實依家警察委任證係咪有「陰陽委任證」？"},{"pid":"018c514ada3b9ff272321ba49edb2401f181ac17","tid":2193063,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9fcc0ceb71b112b72c20cb1663c1a7f272c49f63","tid":2193063,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實依家警察委任證係咪有「陰陽委任證」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"依家黑警件制服啲章多撚過童軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no